txt.en: This coffer, once guarded by a great troll of Khadar-zarâm, now stands alone. You should examine it to see what lies within, and bring the contents to Svanr.
'That is quite the haul, [placeholder]! I am impressed with the goblins' hoard, but they cannot hide valuables from experienced treasure-seekers such as yourself, eh?'
You have discovered treasure that was once guarded by a troll of Khadar-zarâm.
Bring the treasure you found to Svanr
Svanr stands upon the stair of Khadar-zarâm in western Nud-melek.\n\nYou should bring the contents of the coffer you examined to Svanr.
